      <div class="header">
        <h1>Who are we?</h1>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="logo.png" alt="Malaysia Mind Foundation" style="width: 50%;">
        </div>
        <h2>
          The Malaysia Mind Foundation is a charity that works towards creating a society free from discrimination, where all people enjoy positive mental health & well being. Improving individuals, organizations and communities.
        </h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Suicide Prevention</li>
            <li>Improve Well Being</li>
            <li>Information & Advice</li>
            <li>Campaigns & Programmes</li>
            <li>Policy & Advocacy</li>
          </ul>

        <h2>
          Vision & Mission:
        </h2>
          <ul> 
            <li>Vision: Better Mental Health For All</li>
            <li>Mission: The Malaysian Mind Foundation Malaysia works to be the leading provider of inclusive advocacy, awareness, education, support, research and resilience that promote mental health for all.
            </li>
          </ul>	          

        <h2>
          Values:
        </h2>
          <ul> 
            <li>COMPASSION - We hold care, respect, and empathy for all members of the community and emphasis the value of kindness and helping others for mental well being.</li>
            <li>EXCELLENCE - We act with the ambition to respond to the needs of the community and go above and beyond expectations.</li>
            <li>INCLUSION - We celebrate and respect diversity in all its forms and seek to include the whole community in shaping the future for mental health.</li>
            <li>INNOVATION - We act with the initiative to investigate new ideas and explore new approaches, pushing the boundaries of what is achievable.</li>
            <li>INTEGRITY - Regardless of the challenge, we stand by our core values with the well being of the community always in mind.</li>
          </ul>	          
        
